8688eab07455f691ba9abafb43795dfcea31c","tid":904710,"uid":222337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"同樣息口甚至美國仲高息<br />\n你會揀買美債定支債？<br />\n冇人買債個國家會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"好似掉轉咗因果關係<br />\n<br />\n唔係債息升代表債價跌<br />\n債息跌代表債息升咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以加息先會令資產價格下跌<br />\n如果唔夠人買債債息就會升，直到一個equilibrium ，啲人開始買<br />\n如果一直有人買債債息就跌，直到一個equilibrium ，啲人開始唔買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T19:20:41.000Z","msg":"中国国債升幾多跌幾多都無人買<br />\n但債息會影響貸款利息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T22:52:08.000Z","msg":"而家美國債息升，中國人債息跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企業貸款利息升先對企業不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋你第一個statement 可圈可點，即使junk bond 都有人買，只不過人地會畀個好低嘅價(即係好高息)先買<br />\nBond market 好大，國債好難無人買，只係睇下市場會畀咩價格買(價高即息低，價低即息高)<br />\n<br />\n近排美國債息升咁快除咗加息，就係因為美國減稅後收入少咗，要拍賣多啲國債，supply 多咗，令債價跌(即係債息升)"},{"pid":"3b86dae28ad6b9b0921e2e3fafc8a5aebe6a95ea","tid":904710,"uid":116572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef4236e59d35fcac943ee84c8cf77801da7ee2f","tid":904710,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"如果係10年債倒掛都幾大鑊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T22:52:41.000Z","msg":"佢而家係國家同國家比"},{"pid":"172fb41f07911e84822fb2bf2fa04f8adbc28ec2","tid":904710,"uid":155225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e148688eab07455f691ba9abafb43795dfcea31c","tid":904710,"uid":222337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"b5b548b3ae723340a3bfbe670f180d08c5861bb0","tid":904710,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"姐係點<br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"同樣息口甚至美國仲高息<br />\